description: Edge of Fate has raised the stakes in Destiny 2, introducing some of the toughest enemies Guardians have ever faced. But with this newly optimized Mythic Titan build, you’ll have the tools to not just survive — but crush high-level content with confidence.
title: Dominate Destiny 2: Edge of Fate’s Toughest Challenges | Mythic Titan Build

author: IGN
description:
The Toxic Crusaders are back to defend Tromaville against the evil Dr. Killemoff and his army of Radiation Rangers. With local co-op, you can grab up to four friends and take on the forces of Smogula across a variety of vibrant pixel-art levels. Choose from seven playable characters and dive into an action-packed, pun-filled adventure that’ll drag you through the wonderful world of Troma!
Toxic Crusaders launches on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox One, Xbox One Series X/S, Nintendo Switch, and PC on December 4th, 2025.

#IGN #SDCC #ToxicCrusaders
title: Toxic Crusaders - Official Release Date Trailer | SDCC 2025

author: IGN
description:
We checked out FX’s Alien: Earth experience at Comic-Con and got to chat with series creator Noah Hawley. We discussed his approach to the show and what it was like working with such an iconic franchise. FX’s Alien: Earth premieres 8.12 on FX | Hulu.

Presented by FX's Alien: Earth

#IGN #SDCC #AlienEarth
title: How FX’s Alien: Earth Recaptures the Magic of the Alien Franchise: Noah Hawley Interview | SDCC 2025

author: IGN
description:
Ronald D. Moore is known for Battlestar Galactica, Star Trek: The Next Generation, Outlander, For All Mankind, and so much more. And now he's taking on the God of War, Kratos himself, with a live-action series for Amazon.

Moore talks with IGN's Scott Collura about how parent-child relationships appear in all his work, why a video game adaptation like God of War was the right project for him and what he thinks about the latest entries into the Star Trek timeline.

Presented by Mecha BREAK. Available now on Steam and Xbox Series X|S.

#IGN #SDCC #GodofWar
title: God of War: How Ronald D. Moore Is Handling Gaming's Greatest God | SDCC 2025

author: IGN
description:
Star Trek: Strange New Worlds Season 3 and IGN's Scott Collura sits down with cast members Rebecca Romjin, Ethan Peck, Jess Bush, Chistina Chong, and Paul Wesley to discuss what's next for the crew of the Enterprise and its crew at SDCC 2025.

Season 3 of Strange New Worlds sees Una Chin-Riley, Spock, Nurse Chapel, La'an Noonien Singh, and James T. Kirk in brand new adventures along ship Captain Christopher Pike, played by Anson Mount (and his hair). 

We've got murder mysteries, we've got friends learning to be bosses, and we've got the cast breaking down just where they want to see this crazy adventure going before Star Trek: Strange New Worlds comes to an end in Season 5. 

Presented by Mecha BREAK. Available now on Steam and Xbox Series X | S.

#IGN #SDCC #StarTrekStrangeNewWorlds
title: Will Kirk Become Captain at the End of Strange New Worlds? | SDCC 2025

author: IGN
description:
Project Hail Mary may not be hitting theaters until 2026, but famed directors Phil Lord and Christopher Miller, and writer Drew Goddard sat down with IGN at our SDCC studio to chat about the film, Rocky, and the the joys and difficulties of making an adaptation of a beloved story. 

Ryan Gosling stars in the film, taking on the role of Ryland Grace, a former biology teacher and a molecular scientist. He's the science expert on Project Hail Mary's crew. Lord and Miller had the challenge of bringing him to life on screen alongside screenwriter Drew Goddard, who happens to be quite familiar with adapting Andy Weir's work after writing The Martian back in 2015.

You can catch Project Hail Mary in theaters on March 20, 2026.

Presented by FX’s Alien: Earth.

#IGN #SDCC #ProjectHailMary
title: "It's a PC, Not a Mac" Project Hail Mary Directors on Making a Hard Sci-Fi Blockbuster | SDCC 2025

author: IGN
description:
IGN Host Seth Macy gives an inside look at the Predator: Badlands Experience at Comic-Con 2025. There’s awesome props on display, like weapons and relics from the film, a real-life Weyland-Yutani lab, a Spikepod Field, a jungle-themed bar, an animatronic Thia (the synthetic played by Elle Fanning), and even an encounter with Dek’s Father. 

Predator: Badlands releases in theaters on November 7th, 2025.

#IGN #SDCC #PredatorBadlands
title: Inside the Predator: Badlands Experience at Comic-Con | Comic Con 2025

author: IGN
description:

The team behind the film chats diving into the body horror genre head first, and reveal the scenes that were hardest to film because of technical difficulty or the nature of getting the giggles when you're constantly in close quarters.

Presented by Mecha BREAK. Available now on Steam and Xbox Series X | S.

#IGN #SDCC #AlisonBrie #DaveFranco

description:
IGN's San Diego Comic-Con 2025 coverage continues with this deep dive into the brutal world of Killing Floor 3! Join IGN's Alan Knight as he talks with Creative Director Bryan Wynia about the game's intense gore, horror inspirations, and what makes the new specialist classes unique. Plus, see fan reactions to the shocking new gameplay! Killing Floor 3 is available now on PS5, Xbox Series Consoles, and PC.

Presented by Killing Floor 3.

#IGN #SDCC
title: The Gory Future Plans for Killing Floor 3 | SDCC 2025

author: IGN
description:
John Cena and James Gunn came by the IGN stage at San Diego to talk Peacemaker Season 2, but we couldn't stop them from taking over our balcony too! Cena, in full Peacemaker costume, and Gunn thanked the fans gathered on the streets outside the convention center for getting the DCU off to a great start with their reaction to Superman and cheering their heads off for Peacemaker Season 2!

For more Peacemaker, be sure to check out the interviews Jeffrey Vega did with the rest of the cast, including Freddie Stroma, Tim Meadows, Steve Agee, Frank Grillo, Jennifer Holland and Sol Rodriguez.

Presented by FX’s Alien: Earth
title: John Cena and James Gunn Surprise Peacemaker Fans From Our Comic-Con Balcony | SDCC 2025

author: IGN
description:
If it's your first time at Comic-Con as a cosplayer and you're not sure what to bring, pack, or need, then don't worry because Alyson Tabbitha is here to save the day. She walks the floor at San Diego Comic-Con to give you all her favorite tips as well as asking other fellow cosplayers what their tips are for first time cosplayers. 

So let’s avoid running around in a panic and instead have Alyson guide us on what we need to know in order to really savor everything in this special weekend. It only comes once a year, so let’s relish in that cosplay experience.

If you want to see how she built her Zelda cosplay from "The Legend of Zelda: Twilight Princess"  then check out our previous video 
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2TMk5psVtbE

Presented by NHTSA. Speeding Catches Up With You

#IGN #SDCC
title: Tips for Surviving Comic-Con as a Cosplayer - Featuring Alyson Tabbitha

description:
Star Trek: Starfleet Academy will boldly go where no Trek series has gone before: the 32nd Century (not counting a season or two of Discovery).
